reviewText: The best.  My second buy in 20 years.  Instruction for Swing Dancing is simple and concise, being easy to follow and learn.
I loved this set and helped me and my partner learn the different steps.  It has been a great help to us.
Pretty good.  It shows the basic moves very well which is good. If you mastered what is shown on the three tapes.  You'd really know how to swing baby!

Several types of swing dancing, including east coast and west coast.  Pretty basic, just a guy and a lady in a plain room demonstating the steps and going over them from all different angles, nothing fancy.  The 3 tapes  are beginner, intermediate and advanced with different types of swing on  each tape.  This tape was good but nothing to get excited about.
